{"tid":1121454,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"斯里蘭卡恐攻初步調查公布　報復紐西蘭基督城大屠殺","createTime":"2019-04-23T10:26:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-23T13:48:10.000Z","uid":35468,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"3ef971c9b17dddf59cef6190b35bcefd72bcb181","tid":1121454,"uid":35468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T10:26:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4044/d4044682.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4044%2Fd4044682.jpg&h=309d8340&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 聖安東尼聖壇（St Anthony&rsquo;s Shrine）是連環爆炸的發生地之一，內部多處損毀。（圖／路透社，下同）<br />\n<br />\n斯里蘭卡連環爆炸案至今造成321人死亡。斯里蘭卡國防部長維傑瓦丁尼（Ruwan Wijewardene）23日向國會通報初步調查結果，直指這起攻擊事件是由當地伊斯蘭極端分子所為，且是針對紐西蘭基督城清真寺大屠殺事件的報復行動。<br />\n<br />\n法新社報導，根據初步調查結果，此次攻擊是由「國家一神教組織」（National Thowheeth Jama'ath ，NTJ）所策劃，且與印度激進伊斯蘭組織JMI有關。但目前仍未有組織出面宣稱犯案。<br />\n<br />\n維傑瓦丁尼提到，「根據初步調查，斯里蘭卡周日所發生的事件，是針對基督城槍案襲擊穆斯林事件所做的報復行動。」<br />\n<br />\n今年3月15日，紐西蘭基督城2座清真寺遭到槍擊血洗，造成至少50人喪命、數十人受傷。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4041/d4041965.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4041%2Fd4041965.jpg&h=86684a88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4041/d4041964.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4041%2Fd4041964.jpg&h=4ac24a16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4044/d4044681.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4044%2Fd4044681.jpg&h=be1284a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4042/d4042740.jpg[/img\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4042%2Fd4042740.jpg%5B%2Fimg&d=%2FIqeUsS3N0qecbTP5cC9OAzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=e0df95db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4042/d4042740.jpg[/img</a><br />\n<br 